{"word":"H5871 - עַיִן - ʻAyin - ah'-yin - Ain","slug":"H5871","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עַיִן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻAyin"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ah'-yin"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עין</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛ayin</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ah'-yin</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Ain = \"spring\" <ol><li>one of the landmarks on the eastern boundary of Palestine</li><li>one of the southernmost cities of Judah in the Nekeb and allotted to the tribe of Simeon and given to the priests</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H5869\">H5869</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4599\">H4599</a>, <a href=\"#/H5770\">H5770</a>, <a href=\"#/H5869\">H5869</a>, <a href=\"#/H5872\">H5872</a>, <a href=\"#/H5873\">H5873</a>, <a href=\"#/H5874\">H5874</a>, <a href=\"#/H5875\">H5875</a>, <a href=\"#/H5876\">H5876</a>, <a href=\"#/H5877\">H5877</a>, <a href=\"#/H5879\">H5879</a>, <a href=\"#/H5880\">H5880</a>, <a href=\"#/H5881\">H5881</a>, <a href=\"#/H5882\">H5882</a>, <a href=\"#/H5883\">H5883</a>, <a href=\"#/H5884\">H5884</a>, <a href=\"#/H5885\">H5885</a>, <a href=\"#/H5886\">H5886</a>, <a href=\"#/H6044\">H6044</a>, <a href=\"#/H6046\">H6046</a>"}]}